Okay.

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:13.200
Are we live?

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:15.759
Yep.

00:00:15.759 --> 00:00:18.080
Well, good morning.

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:28.470
Are they here yet?

00:00:28.480 --> 00:00:35.256
Yeah, there it is.

00:00:35.256 --> 00:00:36.950
Yep.

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:37.720
They say we're here.

00:00:37.720 --> 00:00:38.840
We've got nine.

00:00:38.840 --> 00:00:41.707
Well, thank you all for joining us today.

00:00:42.747 --> 00:00:43.760
Good morning, family.

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:44.720
Praise the Lord.

00:00:44.720 --> 00:00:46.400
Thank you for joining us.

00:00:46.760 --> 00:00:50.533
You know, I have some things on my heart to pray about tonight.

00:00:50.986 --> 00:00:52.347
It's important.

00:00:52.800 --> 00:01:00.079
You know, we see all the things in the news already about the attacks that we saw in Minnesota today.

00:01:00.079 --> 00:01:05.360
The man tried to hurt the people in the church, but the Lord protected every single one of them.

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:11.289
And that's exactly what we're expecting: for God to show up and intervene like that.

00:01:11.289 --> 00:01:16.479
When that man—I don't know, I guess they hit him with a truck and all that, and then the security guy.

00:01:16.479 --> 00:01:23.173
That's why the Lord—remember, I had you all, I said you must pray about security over your churches in the days ahead.

00:01:23.173 --> 00:01:29.520
And there's a lot of people that come against that, but I'm telling you what the spirit of the Lord said: pray for security in your churches.

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:32.959
And some people can't afford that, but there are some people that can.

00:01:32.959 --> 00:01:37.573
And so that is what the Lord was showing me, and there will be more of this.

00:01:37.573 --> 00:01:39.493
And that was with the man that I saw.

00:01:39.707 --> 00:01:41.540
Most people say, "Well, he lives in America now.

00:01:41.540 --> 00:01:44.457
This powerful, you know, he has a lot of finances.

00:01:44.457 --> 00:01:52.097
" This guy coming against, trying to bring chaos in the spirit realm about mass shootings in churches.

00:01:52.097 --> 00:01:58.280
And then I saw the one in Denver, and I warned you all in the days ahead there.

00:01:58.660 --> 00:02:08.160
I saw a man dressed up in military garb, and he had a bulletproof-looking vest on, and he had a ballistic-looking helmet.

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:13.309
He had a helmet on, and he walked into the crowd, and he started mowing people down with an AR-15.

00:02:13.309 --> 00:02:21.387
And the Lord said, "These things like this, you take your authority and stop these attacks that are planned by the enemy.

00:02:21.387 --> 00:02:24.730
" And it was that place, and I saw some other place.

00:02:25.060 --> 00:02:26.380
I'm trying to remember.

00:02:26.380 --> 00:02:35.307
I see so much, you all, that I have my son and my wife—they have to take notes and help me because I said, "Lord," because He downloads to me all the time.

00:02:35.307 --> 00:02:36.480
It was like today.

00:02:36.480 --> 00:02:48.319
I mean, it's like an open heaven, and I just sit there and just listen, talking to the Father, and He's talking, saying, "Brandon, it's time for My body—for Me to talk to you shouldn't be abnormal.

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:51.760
I want to talk to My body all the time.

00:02:51.760 --> 00:02:56.747
If you're plugged into the electrical socket, you're going to get power, right?

00:02:56.747 --> 00:03:01.519
" So, we're plugged into the Word, we're plugged into Him, and we're hearing Him on a day-to-day basis.

00:03:01.519 --> 00:03:08.360
Are people coming, praying over churches?

00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:08.580
Yeah.

00:03:12.970 --> 00:03:13.160
So, we have some people.

00:03:13.160 --> 00:03:15.760
I just want to make sure people are seeing it.

00:03:17.640 --> 00:03:24.983
I know people are watching the Thunder game, so I didn't want to interrupt it, but I just feel an urgency to pray.

00:03:27.480 --> 00:03:34.213
And so, I thought, "Well, I'm sorry to disrupt your Thunder game, but we have some business to take care of in the spirit realm concerning the days ahead.

00:03:39.067 --> 00:03:39.440
" And it's very serious that the body of Christ does this together.

00:03:42.740 --> 00:03:53.428
I usually just do a video right now, but I feel we're changing things when we're praying as a group, and we're just plowing over the enemy.

00:03:53.428 --> 00:04:05.280
So, what I feel an urgency about right now is still the churches in the days ahead, praying over megachurches, places of worship for mass shootings and things like that.

00:04:05.280 --> 00:04:06.791
Praying for protection over our leaders.

00:04:07.007 --> 00:04:22.436
And I told you all I saw—you know, and I've tried not to always rehearse this—but I saw a mega-preacher in Texas, and I told you to pray for that man, and I said to pray over the preacher in Tampa, and to pray over the person in North Carolina.

00:04:23.760 --> 00:04:27.109
The Lord gives me certain megachurches that were targets, and the Lord said, "Pray over this," but it's more than that.

00:04:31.1000 --> 00:04:36.274
So we look, and right now we have the one in Minnesota, and I didn't even know what that church—I don't even know what denomination it was, but it doesn't matter, folks.

00:04:36.274 --> 00:04:40.453
Do you understand the enemy's coming after everybody he can?

00:04:43.383 --> 00:04:48.690
And so that's why we raise up our voices and pray in the Holy Ghost and put a bloodline around our buildings.

00:04:53.040 --> 00:05:01.698
You need to plead the blood over your church, going around taking your authority and taking it over your children when they go back to school in the fall, praying a hedge of protection over what belongs to us.

00:05:02.107 --> 00:05:05.120
That no weapon formed against you is going to prosper.

00:05:09.698 --> 00:05:10.249
And it is important that you do this not just one time.

00:05:10.249 --> 00:05:12.160
"Well, we did it one time.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:14.853
Well, you know, we talked about it.

00:05:14.853 --> 00:05:18.080
What did we—we did that about a month ago.

00:05:18.080 --> 00:05:22.160
" No, this is something that you do repetitively all the time.

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:28.889
Every day you wake up and you take that seat of authority according to Ephesians.

00:05:35.897 --> 00:05:40.496
You need to read Ephesians, go over Ephesians talking about how we're seated with Him in the heavenlies, and you take that place of authority every single day.

00:05:50.457 --> 00:05:50.834
I do not let one day go by without pleading the blood, taking communion, seeking Him daily.

00:05:53.387 --> 00:06:00.372
This has become—I don't want to say it's a routine, but it is like brushing your teeth, combing your hair (whatever, if you have hair, not like me)—doing this every day.

00:06:00.372 --> 00:06:13.640
And when your kids get ready to go back to school, if they're in public school, go around pleading the blood over things, saying, "Father, as my child is in that building, I put a bloodline.

00:06:22.583 --> 00:06:22.960
We put angels around this building.

00:06:22.960 --> 00:06:34.590
Father, I thank You, Lord, that You said that You send Your angels to keep charge over us, and they will bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against the stone.

00:06:42.064 --> 00:06:42.256
" I believe, Father, that those angels are protecting my babies.

00:06:42.256 --> 00:06:44.697
You must use your authority in the days ahead.

00:06:44.697 --> 00:06:53.600
"Well, we're going to go to the high school football game, we're going to go to the college game, we're going to—" no, no.

00:06:53.600 --> 00:06:55.250
I plead the blood.

00:06:55.250 --> 00:07:03.623
I thank You, Lord, that the blood of Jesus is covering my children, covering us as we go to these sporting events or whatever you plan on doing.

00:07:03.623 --> 00:07:06.811
"We're going to go to a Major League game or whatever.

00:07:06.811 --> 00:07:07.851
" We thank You, Lord.

00:07:13.800 --> 00:07:13.1000
The angels go with me everywhere I go.

00:07:14.200 --> 00:07:15.333
You know, I see these posts on Facebook.

00:07:15.333 --> 00:07:16.053
They'll say, "The angel...

00:07:16.053 --> 00:07:24.240
"—you know, the man's there, and these demons are there trying to mess with them, and the angels come in and start beating up on the demon.

00:07:30.160 --> 00:07:30.320
And I said, "Well, I have to disagree with that post a little bit because my angels never leave.

00:07:30.320 --> 00:07:32.240
They're always there, and they're always ready to defend me.

00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:35.400
I'm not having to call them down to help me out because they're already there.

00:07:35.400 --> 00:07:42.320
" Yes, with their swords and their shields ready, and they're up there going, "Man, I'm ready to bust some devil in the head.

00:07:42.320 --> 00:07:47.929
" They come around here and they're going, "Well, my angels are far off in the distant future.

00:07:47.929 --> 00:07:55.120
" Because that post was like, "Hey, that guy was praying, these devils are there.

00:07:58.639 --> 00:08:01.416
" I don't know if anybody saw that, but they're all there, and these devils are there, and they're growling in the background.

00:08:09.840 --> 00:08:10.010
You could see them, and the guy's in the bed, and he's praying, and all of a sudden the angels show up, and I was like, "No, no, no, no.

00:08:10.010 --> 00:08:10.859
My angels never leave.

00:08:10.859 --> 00:08:12.333
My angels are always on guard.

00:08:12.333 --> 00:08:13.460
" I've got some big ones.

00:08:20.389 --> 00:08:20.659
I always say his name is Big George.

00:08:20.659 --> 00:08:25.599
I've always named him because he's never told me his name.

00:08:26.559 --> 00:08:29.439
And so people go, "Why do you call him Big George?

00:08:29.439 --> 00:08:34.559
" Because I said, "I don't know, it just felt like such an old country name.

00:08:34.559 --> 00:08:36.274
" So I named my angel Big George.

00:08:42.480 --> 00:08:42.759
And people don't like that, but that's my angel.

00:08:51.931 --> 00:08:52.434
I call him what I want to.

00:09:02.674 --> 00:09:03.062
And so Big George is always here, ready to protect me.

00:09:03.062 --> 00:09:08.920
I've seen him multiple times, and he's a big old guy.

00:09:08.920 --> 00:09:10.879
He's a big old sausage-fingers and big hands.

00:09:10.879 --> 00:09:15.337
And it's amazing, you know, the things the Lord will allow me to see.

00:09:15.337 --> 00:09:21.337
I've told you all, He'll even allow me to see when they're protecting me.

00:09:21.337 --> 00:09:35.280
When I'm pumping gas and I'm in a sketchy neighborhood, the angels are there, and I see him there, and I'm—you know, you don't want to be fearful, but you're always on alert, looking around like, "Oh man, I'm in a bad neighborhood.

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:39.480
" And then there's Big George sitting there, standing there, and he's watching out.

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:42.434
He's always at attention, watching over me.

00:09:42.434 --> 00:09:45.760
And I say, "Thank you, Father, for your angels.

00:09:50.560 --> 00:09:50.836
We need to utilize them more and more in the days ahead.

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:00.310
" Angels unaware.

00:10:07.707 --> 00:10:07.911
I believe that God gives his angels to protect us, and I always say, "Father, I commission my angels.

00:10:07.911 --> 00:10:12.960
Father, I thank you that the angels are protecting us.

00:10:12.960 --> 00:10:18.271
Thank you, Lord, that no weapon formed against me is going to prosper.

00:10:29.139 --> 00:10:29.329
" And people, we forget about it.

00:10:29.329 --> 00:10:30.297
It's the unseen realm.

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:33.920
You know, people don't always use that.

00:10:33.920 --> 00:10:36.224
"Oh well, you know, the unseen realm, whatever.

00:10:36.224 --> 00:10:37.320
" No, no, no.

00:10:41.088 --> 00:10:41.680
I believe that every one of us has angels that watch over us.

00:10:41.680 --> 00:10:44.293
Believers, believing believers, I believe they're watching.

00:10:44.293 --> 00:10:49.400
Angels are watching over your children; they're watching over you.

00:10:53.560 --> 00:10:58.373
And it's time we become more strong about doing that, not sitting back going, "Well, you know, every once in a while.

00:10:58.373 --> 00:11:02.830
" No, I do it every day, every day, all the time.

00:11:02.830 --> 00:11:06.370
Even when I'm driving: "Angels, protect us as we drive.

00:11:06.370 --> 00:11:27.257
Father, I cover us with the mighty name of Jesus over our house, over our car as we drive down the highway, over our tires, over everything, that, Father, we make it there safe and we make it back safe, and that, Father, we are always covered by your blood and your angels are watching over us.

00:11:36.194 --> 00:11:36.411
" And that's what you're going to have to do in the days ahead more and more.

00:11:44.480 --> 00:11:44.900
That's what Psalm 91 even talks about, that he gives his angels charge over us.

00:11:47.839 --> 00:11:55.200
So, I'm trying to give you some encouragement today that we're not going to be afraid of the terror by night, nor for the arrow that flieth by day.

00:11:55.200 --> 00:12:05.720
We're not going to be afraid of those things because Jesus Christ has sent his angels to protect us, and he has given his word that we could use it as a weapon.

00:12:05.720 --> 00:12:06.639
It's our sword.

00:12:11.333 --> 00:12:11.627
And so, that's what we're going to do.

00:12:17.089 --> 00:12:17.339
And yeah, I see these things and what the Lord shows me is coming.

00:12:29.519 --> 00:12:29.759
But I'm telling you folks, the believers, us, the people that are watching this broadcast, I believe we have a special covering.

00:12:31.691 --> 00:12:32.446
And I said I'm not participating in mass casualties.

00:12:32.446 --> 00:12:34.693
We're not going to participate in a financial disaster.

00:12:34.693 --> 00:12:37.307
We're always going to be above and not beneath.

00:12:37.307 --> 00:12:40.216
We're going to go through and not go under.

00:12:40.216 --> 00:12:53.519
I don't know about you, ladies and gentlemen, but I know that God is able to protect me, and he's an ever-present help in a time of need, and he's going to watch over us.

00:12:53.749 --> 00:12:56.906
And so I try to encourage you.

00:12:56.906 --> 00:12:58.765
Yeah, these volcanoes I've seen erupting.

00:12:58.765 --> 00:13:00.582
I've seen earthquakes in diverse places.

00:13:00.582 --> 00:13:03.520
I've seen major storms, mega-major hurricanes in the days ahead.

00:13:04.260 --> 00:13:17.900
I saw a great hurricane coming, and I saw it being seeded, and I saw the eyewall was so tight and it was very, very strong, kind of like the one that hit Florida and went up through North Carolina and caused all that damage.

00:13:17.900 --> 00:13:22.520
I'm talking about a major hurricane coming, and the Lord said, "Poke the eyewall out.

00:13:22.520 --> 00:13:27.269
" Don't pray for it to go to Fort Myers or to Tampa or to Destin or whatever.

00:13:27.269 --> 00:13:31.577
When we take authority over it, we poke the eyewall out.

00:13:31.577 --> 00:13:33.680
Make it fall apart, Lord.

00:13:33.680 --> 00:13:39.440
Because, you know, I always see believers when they're praying in that area: "Oh, go this way.

00:13:39.440 --> 00:13:40.480
Go that way.

00:13:40.480 --> 00:13:42.308
No, no, no, go down here.

00:13:45.280 --> 00:13:45.600
Don't go down here.

00:13:45.600 --> 00:13:52.182
" But what we need to do is use our faith and say, "Father, you weaken that thing.

00:13:52.182 --> 00:13:56.519
It's a tropical storm now, or a depression, or whatever.

00:13:56.519 --> 00:13:59.640
We're not going to have a major hurricane this year.

00:13:59.640 --> 00:14:01.566
" That's the kind of authority.

00:14:01.566 --> 00:14:05.600
"As he is, so are we in this world.

00:14:05.600 --> 00:14:07.413
" That's what the Bible says.

00:14:07.413 --> 00:14:13.880
Now, people would argue with that all the time, but that's what the Bible says: "As he is, so are we in this world.

00:14:17.480 --> 00:14:21.234
" And if Jesus could do it, he gave us the authority to do it also.

00:14:21.234 --> 00:14:21.851
Why?

00:14:21.851 --> 00:14:24.479
Because he dwells on the inside of me.

00:14:24.479 --> 00:14:31.725
And I believe we can pray over the storms and tell them, "Peace, be still," just like Jesus did in that boat.

00:14:35.097 --> 00:14:35.566
He was resting, and the disciples were freaking out, but he wasn't.

00:14:36.034 --> 00:14:37.440
He was asleep.

00:14:50.180 --> 00:14:54.879
So there was a peace there.

00:14:57.573 --> 00:15:02.980
And when you have that inward peace, that peace that passes all understanding, that's why I say we've got to follow our peace in everything we do.

00:15:02.980 --> 00:15:06.400
If it costs you your peace, it's too expensive.

00:15:06.400 --> 00:15:06.880
Yes.

00:15:06.880 --> 00:15:09.200
But I say that's why you follow your peace.

00:15:09.822 --> 00:15:14.020
And people, you know, that's why I say I don't make a big decision until I have peace.

00:15:14.020 --> 00:15:16.996
We talk about it all the time.

00:15:16.996 --> 00:15:25.591
If it's financial, say if it's buying a car or maybe a house or a job offer or whatever, you follow your peace.

00:15:25.591 --> 00:15:32.133
And if you don't have peace, don't do it, because that Prince of Peace is dwelling on the inside of you.

00:15:41.303 --> 00:15:49.152
And if you have that inward check, and that's the Holy Spirit scratching you saying, "Don't do that.

00:15:49.152 --> 00:15:52.789
You're making a bad choice right now.

00:15:52.789 --> 00:15:56.649
You're about to make a really dumb choice.

00:15:56.649 --> 00:16:06.822
Don't do that," and you go, "Well, you know, hon" — so I told her, I said, "You know, I just don't feel peace about going to that place.

00:16:06.822 --> 00:16:09.782
I don't feel peace about going to that vacation spot or whatever.

00:16:09.782 --> 00:16:11.739
Let's follow the voice of the Lord.

00:16:24.210 --> 00:16:24.620
" And that's why I say I always inquire of the Lord in everything I do.

00:16:24.620 --> 00:16:29.653
No matter where I go, I say, "Is it meant for me to go there today?

00:16:32.107 --> 00:16:36.263
" And I believe as the day approaches and it gets darker and darker like I've told you is coming, we always ask him every morning.

00:16:36.263 --> 00:16:43.795
Father, I thank you, Lord, because the people on 9/11, there were a lot of people that were supposed to be there and they didn't show up that day.

00:16:43.795 --> 00:16:47.379
But are they the ones that inquired of the Lord?

00:16:47.379 --> 00:16:48.909
"Father, I don't feel that peace today.

00:16:48.909 --> 00:16:59.484
" We heard a story by Brother Hagin, and he was talking about one of his members, that the pastors were praying over some of the members and they said, "I feel something really bad.

00:17:04.709 --> 00:17:04.846
We need to pray.

00:17:04.846 --> 00:17:11.439
" And they knew five members were out on vacation, so they kept interceding all night long.

00:17:23.1000 --> 00:17:24.240
And I want to make this short for y'all because I know you have things you've got to do, but I feel I'm supposed to tell you this.

00:17:24.240 --> 00:17:33.999
They started praying and they interceded for hours, and they still couldn't get a release, and they thought, "Man, something's really wrong still.

00:17:42.524 --> 00:17:42.907
" And so these two prayer warriors, the pastors of the church, kept praying for their members of the church.

00:17:55.703 --> 00:17:56.000
Well, they stopped after three or four times of getting up in the middle of the night, kept praying.

00:17:56.000 --> 00:17:59.780
He said, "Well, whoever this is, Lord, let them have a dream.

00:17:59.780 --> 00:18:08.640
Let them have a dream and tell them in their dream whatever the caution is, what we're feeling and we're interceding.

00:18:08.640 --> 00:18:19.600
" So the next day, their children's church worker, one of the people there over the children's church, went to the job site.

00:18:31.371 --> 00:18:31.600
And he told the guy, because the guy that was normally there didn't come in to work that day, and he said, "Hey, why don't you go...

00:18:31.600 --> 00:18:39.840
" — there was an oil rig — and he told him, he said, "I want you to go up there and help out with this lift or whatever.

00:18:40.434 --> 00:18:41.325
You do it instead.

00:18:41.622 --> 00:18:42.673
You do it instead.

00:18:45.360 --> 00:18:52.103
" And he said, "Last night, I had a dream, and in the dream I saw that wire right there break free, and it cut my head off and it fell to the ground.

00:18:52.103 --> 00:18:55.600
So, I don't feel peace about going up there.

00:19:05.508 --> 00:19:05.771
" And so he told the guy, "I'm sorry, I can't do it.

00:19:11.573 --> 00:19:14.871
" Well, the other guy, who was from the church across town that did not believe in the baptism of the Holy Ghost and didn't believe all this stuff, he said, "I'm not superstitious.

00:19:14.871 --> 00:19:17.280
I'll go up there and do the job.

00:19:17.280 --> 00:19:33.120
" So he ran up the side of that thing, and five minutes into it, the wire snapped and cut that man's head off, and it bumped that guy who was praying in the spirit in his back.

00:19:44.709 --> 00:19:45.063
So it was a leading of the Lord trying to warn them that there was something wrong with it, but he went with his peace.

00:19:45.063 --> 00:19:54.080
Now the other guy didn't believe anything, and, you know, things happened with Christians, but one prayed in tongues.

00:19:54.080 --> 00:19:56.840
Yeah, one prayed in tongues, one prayed in the spirit.

00:19:56.840 --> 00:20:01.646
Sometimes we don't know what we're supposed to be praying, right?

00:20:01.646 --> 00:20:05.360
What is this that I feel?

00:20:05.360 --> 00:20:06.510
What is this caution?

00:20:10.600 --> 00:20:11.067
And so when praying in tongues, you have the gift of praying in tongues.

00:20:15.679 --> 00:20:15.809
And that's what we pray in the spirit all the time.

00:20:15.809 --> 00:20:17.670
Diana and I pray in the spirit all the time.

00:20:20.400 --> 00:20:28.800
And not saying that one's better than the other, but one's tapped into the spirit realm a little bit more than the other, you know, and that's what I'm trying to tell y'all.

00:20:28.800 --> 00:20:40.355
Being baptized in the Holy Ghost, but I felt an urgency following that peace because the other man followed the peace, and the other man didn't know peace.

00:20:40.355 --> 00:20:42.159
He's not here anymore, of course.

00:20:42.159 --> 00:20:44.520
And the other guy, he was a teaching superintendent.

00:20:44.520 --> 00:20:47.330
He was over the children's ministry, and his life was spared.

00:20:58.320 --> 00:20:58.514
But if the boss would have listened to him and said, 'You know what?

00:20:58.514 --> 00:21:08.411
We should probably check that wire then,' you know, we probably should check that wire, he would have found out that there was something wrong with it.

00:21:08.411 --> 00:21:11.440
But just follow it.

00:21:11.440 --> 00:21:17.086
What I'm trying to tell you is don't—the reason I brought all that up is don't ignore the peace.

00:21:17.086 --> 00:21:21.671
Follow it in the days ahead, and it will keep you and protect you.

00:21:27.480 --> 00:21:27.780
You must follow the peace of God.

00:21:33.520 --> 00:21:50.009
And when we go through all these things that are coming, I pray, 'Father, I'm always in the right place at the right time doing exactly what you've asked me to do for that day, and I will not miss it because you said that your children will hear your voice, a strange voice they will not follow.

00:21:50.009 --> 00:21:52.604
' And that's what I expect from it.

00:21:55.919 --> 00:21:56.179
I expect to hear you, Father.

00:21:56.179 --> 00:22:04.000
I expect when people say, 'Well, I don't hear God like you, Brandon.

00:22:04.000 --> 00:22:05.600
I don't hear God like you, Diana.

00:22:05.600 --> 00:22:06.440
' Yes, you do.

00:22:13.783 --> 00:22:14.091
You know what?

00:22:19.456 --> 00:22:19.648
It didn't come overnight.

00:22:24.667 --> 00:22:25.013
It comes by practice.

00:22:30.496 --> 00:22:30.800
It comes by—'faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the word of God.

00:22:30.800 --> 00:22:33.876
' But hearing his voice, too, comes by deliberately trying.

00:22:35.813 --> 00:22:36.240
And I say, 'Lord, I'm practicing your presence today.

00:22:36.240 --> 00:22:44.777
' I'm not saying I have it right all the time, but you know, as you grow, you get better at something.

00:22:44.777 --> 00:22:46.578
It's like riding a bike, walking, or whatever.

00:22:49.109 --> 00:22:50.819
Like a child, you keep falling, but you keep getting yourself back up.

00:23:00.000 --> 00:23:00.320
And people say, 'Well, you know, I'm embarrassed to say that or that.

00:23:00.320 --> 00:23:02.240
' No, no, no, folks.

00:23:02.240 --> 00:23:05.700
I've missed it a lot in the past.

00:23:05.700 --> 00:23:06.720
But you know what happens?

00:23:12.613 --> 00:23:14.343
The more you practice, the more you stand, the more you read his word, you're going to get better and better at it.

00:23:15.394 --> 00:23:18.540
And I say, 'Lord, I thank you.

00:23:18.540 --> 00:23:20.366
Man, that was embarrassing.

00:23:20.366 --> 00:23:22.592
' Well, that's all right.

00:23:22.592 --> 00:23:25.306
I pick myself up, brush yourself off, and just keep walking it out.

00:23:25.306 --> 00:23:28.263
Nobody's perfect, and nobody's going to get it right 99.

00:23:28.263 --> 00:23:30.700
9% of the time, 100% of the time, whatever.

00:23:32.040 --> 00:23:32.220
I'm just saying that's how you practice.

00:23:32.220 --> 00:23:42.690
You practice the voice and hearing the voice of God by his word, getting in the word, listening to him, and you say, 'Lord,' you may say, 'Well, I'm just going to keep doing it.

00:23:42.690 --> 00:23:50.537
' That's how you get good at it.

00:23:50.537 --> 00:23:55.244
How does a professional basketball player become the best and become MVP?

00:23:55.244 --> 00:23:56.230
Practice, practice.

00:23:56.230 --> 00:23:58.240
It's the same with football and everything else.

00:23:58.240 --> 00:24:01.929
I'm just comparing it to sports because that's what you maybe can relate with.

00:24:01.929 --> 00:24:05.211
A race car driver gets to be the best because he practices.

00:24:05.211 --> 00:24:09.740
And as you practice, you become, like I said, a champion.

00:24:10.736 --> 00:24:14.320
The only way you're going to become a champion is if you become good at the fundamentals.

00:24:19.190 --> 00:24:19.460
You have to become good at the fundamentals first so that you hear the voice of God.

00:24:19.460 --> 00:24:24.000
And the fundamentals of Christianity are going to church, reading your Bible, and praying.

00:24:24.000 --> 00:24:28.159
And those are the fundamentals, but you go back to the ABCs.

00:24:28.159 --> 00:24:30.008
Everybody wants to go to algebra and skip the ABCs.

00:24:31.919 --> 00:24:34.720
But everything in Christianity is based off of the ABCs first, and that's how you keep going from glory to glory to glory.

00:24:34.720 --> 00:24:41.039
But if you forget your fundamentals and the ABCs, you're not going to remember how to do the algebra equation.

00:24:48.571 --> 00:24:48.823
And you're going to be looking at it going, 'Man, I don't know.

00:24:48.823 --> 00:24:57.120
' And that's why I say if I get off track and you're going, 'Man, I feel I'm a little lost here,' go back to the basics.

00:25:08.000 --> 00:25:08.480
What got you there in the first place?

00:25:08.480 --> 00:25:11.378
'Well, I'm a little off today.

00:25:11.378 --> 00:25:12.373
What's going on?

00:25:12.373 --> 00:25:14.272
' No, it's not panic time.

00:25:14.272 --> 00:25:15.424
It's go-back-to-the-basics time.

00:25:23.248 --> 00:25:23.616
Because back to the basics, the ABCs, is the foundation.

00:25:36.000 --> 00:25:41.270
And if you—the foundation is the word, and you get this beautiful book down inside of you and you don't turn away from it, and you get down and pray, that's when you're not a goose in the fog anymore, and you're all of a sudden going, 'Hey, I found my heading.

00:25:42.818 --> 00:25:44.773
I know where I'm going now because I went back to the basics.

00:25:44.773 --> 00:25:48.080
' But people try to make things in Christianity too complicated.

00:25:48.080 --> 00:25:50.559
But he made it so that a child can do it.

00:25:56.919 --> 00:25:57.419
Your five-year-old little child can have a relationship with the Lord and hear him every day.

00:26:07.440 --> 00:26:07.760
He didn't make it where, 'Well, you know, you're not a super adult Christian, so only the people who are college Christians can hear the voice of the Lord.

00:26:07.760 --> 00:26:10.960
' No, he made it so that a child can listen to him.

00:26:22.189 --> 00:26:22.459
A child can live by faith.

00:26:22.459 --> 00:26:24.080
God didn't make it hard.

00:26:24.080 --> 00:26:25.130
We make it hard.

00:26:25.130 --> 00:26:28.160
'Well, you know, God doesn't talk to me.

00:26:28.160 --> 00:26:30.948
' No, he does talk to you.

00:26:37.129 --> 00:26:37.351
I say my Father is always there, and he's willing to talk to me because why?

00:26:43.760 --> 00:26:44.071
He loves me.

00:26:44.071 --> 00:26:55.279
If we really, truly realized how much God loves us, if we really, truly realized how much he cares for us—and people go, 'Well, does God love me?

00:26:55.279 --> 00:26:56.599
' Yes, yes.

00:26:56.599 --> 00:27:03.160
He loved you so much that he gave his Son to die for you.

00:27:03.160 --> 00:27:04.389
That's enough.

00:27:04.389 --> 00:27:06.479
I mean, that's huge.

00:27:06.479 --> 00:27:11.260
If he never did anything else for you, he did everything.

00:27:11.260 --> 00:27:21.760
Even if, you know, we are always waiting for God to do something more, well, God already did it all.

00:27:21.760 --> 00:27:24.240
We just have to receive it by faith.

00:27:26.764 --> 00:27:35.074
And there are so many people that think, 'Well, you know, why does God not take care of these devil situations and all the things that are going on in my life?

00:27:35.074 --> 00:27:37.413
' He said, 'It is finished.

00:27:37.413 --> 00:27:41.542
' He doesn't have to die again for you.

00:27:41.542 --> 00:27:42.799
He's already died once.

00:27:42.799 --> 00:27:46.343
If he said, 'It is finished,' everything he set out to do was done.

00:27:46.343 --> 00:28:00.480
So all you have to do is receive it by faith and say, 'I stand on the word, and I'm going to do what the Bible says I can do, and I'm going to take what the devil stole from me, and you're not going to ramrod me anymore, sucker.

00:28:00.480 --> 00:28:02.000
You're underneath my feet.

00:28:02.000 --> 00:28:07.973
' And that's why I try to tell y'all to get a backbone like a crowbar.

00:28:07.973 --> 00:28:12.329
Because if you don't, the devil comes as a roaring lion seeking whom he may devour.

00:28:12.329 --> 00:28:14.720
Who are the ones he can't devour?

00:28:14.720 --> 00:28:19.520
The ones who know who they are.

00:28:19.520 --> 00:28:32.080
And they take their authority, and like Ephesians says, they say, 'Hey, man, you ain't robbing me.

00:28:32.080 --> 00:28:34.990
And if you do, you're paying me back double.

00:28:35.680 --> 00:28:37.520
You're paying me back double.

00:28:37.520 --> 00:28:47.407
' And eventually, you'll get too expensive for the devil to mess with.

00:28:51.146 --> 00:29:08.559
You start using your authority, and you start calling those things that be not as though they were, and you walk by faith, you start actually doing what the word of God says you can do, and you can have what the word of God says you can have.

00:29:22.710 --> 00:29:22.986
When you start doing that, you'll be too expensive for the devil to mess with.

00:29:22.986 --> 00:29:26.560
He's going to go, 'Man, they know who they are.

00:29:26.560 --> 00:29:31.333
I'm going to mess with that guy over there; he doesn't know who he is.

00:29:31.333 --> 00:29:37.370
' Because that's what the Bible says: he comes as a roaring lion seeking whom he may devour.

00:29:37.370 --> 00:29:38.760
That means he can't devour everybody.

00:29:38.760 --> 00:29:42.799
He can only devour the people who don't know who they are.

00:29:42.799 --> 00:29:45.232
And they go, "But he'll challenge it.

00:29:45.232 --> 00:29:49.440
" I'm not saying he won't challenge a roaring, lying lion.

00:29:49.440 --> 00:29:52.544
He's a liar.

00:29:52.544 --> 00:29:55.964
He doesn't tell any truth.

00:29:55.964 --> 00:29:59.632
He may try, but he can't.

00:29:59.632 --> 00:30:09.984
If you stand on the Word and put that supersuit on called the Armor of God, that's your super clothes.

00:30:09.984 --> 00:30:10.880
Everybody can get this in you.

00:30:10.880 --> 00:30:14.903
Yes, the Word of God, but it's your super clothes.

00:30:27.440 --> 00:30:27.840
That's what I was trying to say.

00:30:27.840 --> 00:30:31.600
It's like you're a superhero with your super clothes on.

00:30:31.600 --> 00:30:36.840
Most people don't want to put maybe your gospel shoes on or whatever.

00:30:36.840 --> 00:30:47.733
Maybe you just have your helmet on, but bring your sword every once in a while, but you don't put the whole Armor of God on.

00:30:47.733 --> 00:30:52.680
You just put a part of it.

00:30:52.680 --> 00:31:01.900
But like I said, I want to operate in the fruits of the Spirit.

00:31:02.580 --> 00:31:05.920
And the Lord even today is saying, "Brandon, you've got to get more foundational love.

00:31:05.920 --> 00:31:08.046
You've got to walk it out in love.

00:31:08.046 --> 00:31:08.960
Love never fails.

00:31:08.960 --> 00:31:12.926
When people talk bad to you, when people treat you bad, love never fails.

00:31:14.297 --> 00:31:16.739
" And that's something I deal with all the time, y'all.

00:31:16.739 --> 00:31:20.999
"Well, I'm not going to talk to them today.

00:31:20.999 --> 00:31:21.399
" No.

00:31:25.376 --> 00:31:25.632
Lord said, "Love them.

00:31:26.400 --> 00:31:30.000
" "I don't want to be around them today," you know, Sister So-and-So.

00:31:43.740 --> 00:31:44.250
Lord said, "Love them.

00:31:52.373 --> 00:31:52.560
" "I don't want to go," you know.

00:31:55.893 --> 00:32:00.959
But people don't want to hear that.

00:32:00.959 --> 00:32:11.333
But that's what it takes because He abides in me and His words remain in me.

00:32:11.333 --> 00:32:19.246
If you abide in me and my words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.

00:32:22.026 --> 00:32:23.760
And that's why I say, when you say, "Why don't my prayers get answered?

00:32:23.760 --> 00:32:27.280
" it is because you're not abiding in the Word.

00:32:30.582 --> 00:32:30.914
Pray the Word.

00:32:30.914 --> 00:32:36.870
Find scripture that pertains to what you're believing God for, whether it's healing, deliverance, whatever you may need, find something.

00:32:45.990 --> 00:32:47.573
And you say, "Well, I don't know how to do that.

00:32:47.573 --> 00:32:49.590
" Google it, I don't know, find something.

00:32:54.445 --> 00:32:54.753
And there's a list of scriptures on the Bible app that I have.

00:33:01.460 --> 00:33:01.800
And I'll go out, whatever I'm overcoming that day, whatever I need—peace, passing understanding, whatever—and they have all of them.

00:33:01.800 --> 00:33:12.216
And I go, "Okay, well, I'm just going to go through each one of these, and I'm just going to find the scripture, and I'm just going to meditate on that all day long by renewing your mind.

00:33:12.216 --> 00:33:16.320
" Renew your mind by the Word of God.

00:33:16.320 --> 00:33:17.160
Yes, finances.

00:33:17.160 --> 00:33:18.200
Find financial scriptures.

00:33:18.200 --> 00:33:25.794
"Father, my God will supply all my needs according to His riches in glory by Christ Jesus.

00:33:25.794 --> 00:33:27.291
" Well, He said He'd do it.

00:33:30.914 --> 00:33:31.143
I believe it.

00:33:34.373 --> 00:33:35.860
That settles it.

00:33:35.860 --> 00:33:41.799
I'm not going to be moved by what I see anymore.

00:33:41.799 --> 00:33:43.240
I believe it.

00:33:43.240 --> 00:33:43.510
I receive it.

00:33:56.559 --> 00:33:57.269
And that settles it.

00:33:57.269 --> 00:33:58.689
Period.

00:34:02.240 --> 00:34:03.227
And I'm going to live by faith.

00:34:03.227 --> 00:34:07.369
Either you believe it and you're a believer, or you don't.

00:34:07.369 --> 00:34:15.560
If you don't believe it, it's not going to come to pass.

00:34:15.560 --> 00:34:17.149
I'm not a doubter.

00:34:17.149 --> 00:34:18.149
I'm an overcomer.

00:34:23.467 --> 00:34:23.653
And I believe I'm going to live by faith and not by sight.

00:34:23.653 --> 00:34:24.027
Yes.

00:34:28.120 --> 00:34:28.340
So that was my little thing for you today.

00:34:28.340 --> 00:34:31.066
Now, what's the Lord telling us to pray for?

00:34:31.066 --> 00:34:36.213
I don't know where that all came from, but you got that for free.

00:34:45.031 --> 00:34:45.413
He said to pray over the Strait of Hormuz.

00:34:45.413 --> 00:34:49.412
Yes, this is what I saw in the spirit.

00:34:49.412 --> 00:34:54.769
Even the last time He said, "You must pray over this.

00:34:57.306 --> 00:34:59.560
" I saw an uprising in that area, trying to block the oil and supplies.

00:34:59.560 --> 00:35:06.760
And the Lord said, "I saw the United States Navy getting involved in this area.

00:35:06.760 --> 00:35:08.343
" Now, I saw battleships.

00:35:08.343 --> 00:35:11.680
I saw Iran being put back, scattered like roaches.

00:35:11.680 --> 00:35:21.257
It's important that we pray over this because, remember, I told you all I saw oil going above—and this is not financial advice.

00:35:21.257 --> 00:35:23.520
Am I telling you to buy oil stocks?

00:35:24.480 --> 00:35:26.930
I didn't even realize you could until somebody emailed, "Well, you're giving me...

00:35:26.930 --> 00:35:30.229
" No, I'm telling you what I saw in the spirit.

00:35:30.229 --> 00:35:33.740
Now, it's the same thing like this man said, "You know what?

00:35:41.769 --> 00:35:41.991
When you were talking about the Asian man, I went to Las Vegas and put all this money down on it.

00:35:50.250 --> 00:35:50.468
" And when it didn't happen, I said, "I didn't even know there was such a thing as gambling.

00:35:50.468 --> 00:35:53.866
" These people, I'm like, "You all need to get born again.

00:35:53.866 --> 00:35:54.861
" This is serious.

00:35:54.861 --> 00:35:57.623
I'm just ignorant to this stuff, folks.

00:35:57.623 --> 00:35:59.421
I'm telling you, follow the voice of God.

00:36:09.458 --> 00:36:09.707
So when I see the oil, I saw in the ticker—it was a ticker in front of me—I saw $200 a barrel.

00:36:09.707 --> 00:36:11.611
"Do I need that off my face?

00:36:11.611 --> 00:36:12.903
" "On your lips right there.

00:36:12.903 --> 00:36:13.429
Thanks.

00:36:13.429 --> 00:36:14.217
" "Other side.

00:36:14.217 --> 00:36:15.120
" "This side.

00:36:15.120 --> 00:36:15.760
Thanks.

00:36:15.760 --> 00:36:17.040
" "No, this side.

00:36:17.040 --> 00:36:17.720
" "Yeah, that side.

00:36:17.720 --> 00:36:18.230
I forget.

00:36:18.230 --> 00:36:21.218
It's like a mirror to you.

00:36:21.218 --> 00:36:22.284
" "Mirror to God, it's live.

00:36:22.284 --> 00:36:22.640
Okay.

00:36:22.640 --> 00:36:23.200
Thank you, Jesus.

00:36:29.920 --> 00:36:30.240
" "You didn't know there was such a thing.

00:36:30.240 --> 00:36:31.840
That's what you're saying.

00:36:31.840 --> 00:36:32.423
" "Yeah.

00:36:32.423 --> 00:36:33.211
Thanks, Brad.

00:36:33.211 --> 00:36:34.000
Oh, Diana.

00:36:34.000 --> 00:36:34.978
Well, I appreciate it.

00:36:35.760 --> 00:36:37.935
It's like saying, 'Do I have a booger in my nose?

00:36:42.240 --> 00:36:42.480
I don't want it there either, you know.

00:36:42.480 --> 00:36:45.378
' Well, okay, we're just real.

00:36:45.378 --> 00:36:47.152
Where did I wind up in this thing?

00:36:47.152 --> 00:36:48.336
So, what was...

00:36:55.800 --> 00:36:56.020
Oh, so you just tell them what you see.

00:36:59.830 --> 00:37:00.061
Yeah, I just tell you what I see.

00:37:00.061 --> 00:37:11.967
So, I see about the oil and the ticker and all the things, and I saw $200, and I saw the price of gas going above $9.

00:37:16.240 --> 00:37:29.653
And I saw in the vision it went from coast to coast, and the Lord said the average gas price in the vision when I was praying, I saw it was like $8 a gallon.

00:37:29.653 --> 00:37:31.160
And then I saw...

00:37:52.320 --> 00:37:52.537
and I just tell you details about it.

00:37:57.653 --> 00:37:57.880
It kept going, and it was moving really fast in front of me.

00:38:02.880 --> 00:38:03.310
This means it was a prolonged period of time.

00:38:15.395 --> 00:38:15.670
It was like several weeks.

00:38:23.839 --> 00:38:24.109
And then I kept hearing in the vision, I could hear, 'Drill, baby, drill.

00:38:24.109 --> 00:38:26.000
' And I saw the Mediterranean.

00:38:29.874 --> 00:38:30.091
I saw Gaza.

00:38:31.460 --> 00:38:36.477
I saw great wealth in Gaza underneath the water.

00:38:52.880 --> 00:38:53.220
And I saw massive amounts of gas reserves, big things.

00:38:54.471 --> 00:38:56.860
And then I saw a number come up in front of me.

00:38:58.920 --> 00:38:59.580
It was a ticker in front of me again.

00:38:59.800 --> 00:39:04.267
And I could see billions of dollars coming to Israel from the ground in Gaza.

00:39:04.267 --> 00:39:07.771
Billions, and they knew the oil is in the ground.

00:39:07.771 --> 00:39:10.320
Well, that could come across controversial, but that's what I see.

00:39:10.320 --> 00:39:13.383
Then I see a pipeline in America being opened up again.

00:39:28.669 --> 00:39:28.858
I see great wealth coming through this big pipeline in America, working on this pipeline again.

00:39:37.360 --> 00:39:37.600
And I see great wealth in the Gulf of Mexico again, lots and lots of oil.

00:39:39.060 --> 00:39:42.160
And I saw a funding of finances with oil concerning America and the petro dollar.

00:39:48.650 --> 00:39:48.900
And it was helping balance the budget somehow.

00:39:50.903 --> 00:39:54.960
And then I saw crypto and this new digital stuff, and it was all being worked on.

00:39:55.440 --> 00:39:59.484
And it was, like I said, on a thin line.

00:40:00.559 --> 00:40:06.709
And the Lord said there has to be a foundation because it's like the Wild West right now.

00:40:09.227 --> 00:40:15.920
But there will be regulations and foundation in the days ahead, and this will be something that will be part of the Beast system in the future.

00:40:16.249 --> 00:40:28.339
And it just shows this is how I pray, and He just shows me stuff, and I just keep practicing His presence, and this is what He shows me, and He tells me all this stuff.

00:40:36.177 --> 00:40:36.533
Then He tells me about, you know, and here I see again this Hormuz thing, Hormuz or whatever it is, these words.

00:40:36.533 --> 00:40:45.008
I see all that, and then the Lord shows me that mountain in Iran that they just blew up last night that I told you I saw on Saturday.

00:40:45.200 --> 00:40:55.840
And I said, "I see this on Saturday," but I saw them taking biological things out of that mountain, big 50-gallon drums, putting them in the back of a truck.

00:40:59.200 --> 00:40:59.440
I can tell you where they put them, too.

00:41:08.576 --> 00:41:08.752
And the Lord warns me of these things.

00:41:08.752 --> 00:41:09.984
He says, "Pray for the people.

00:41:09.984 --> 00:41:11.875
Pray for them because they use them on the people.

00:41:13.252 --> 00:41:13.803
